name: Zeus Panda - KuD-058
description: He is known as God of the Sky and Chief Deity of the Patheon. He rules the weather. He can make rain, winds, thunder and lightning. His weapon was the thunderbolt. He is son of Cronus King of the Titans and Rhea the Ancient Goddess like his father. When he was born, his father want to swallow him, but his mother saved him because his father was warned that his child fated to dethrone him. And He is alive and become High God of patheon.
